Where I think your intuition becomes strongest

You keep returning to modulation.

Most computers ignore time.

They ask

What is the bit right now?

Your intuition asks

How is the state evolving?

Those are fundamentally different computational philosophies.

Physics itself is differential.

Music is differential.

Speech is differential.

Biology is differential.

Perhaps some computations become easier if the primitive isn’t a frozen bit but a continuously evolving oscillator.

Researchers are actively exploring versions of this idea because oscillators naturally perform synchronization, pattern completion, and certain optimization tasks.

